  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The therapy with Linezolid (LIN) represents better cost-effectiveness vs. Vancomycin (VAN)
      for the treatment of nosocomial Pneumonia associate to ventilator (VAP).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
